00:16:05.880 --> 00:16:07.590
- [Derek] But there were also major flaws

00:16:07.590 --> 00:16:08.850
with vacuum tubes.

00:16:08.850 --> 00:16:10.830
The filaments always needed to be heated,

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:14.070
